                "image": {
                    "url": "https://vc4test.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/process.png"
                },
                "title": "Usability",
                "text": "<p>Information management and promoting product usability are the key components of B2B marketing campaigns. Ecommerce software should provide a promotion service engine with tools to optimize and drive conversions, as well as intuitive controls that can be used without training. Clear ticketing system, simple event and campaign creation, optimized content management and rapid order management are the groundwork for an online store. Stats tracking and reporting allow you to have an insight into the running of your B2B businesses online and to drive specific campaigns. You can&#39;t control what you can&#39;t measure. The monitoring of business metrics must be detailed and easily accessible.</p>\n"
